snippet.title: This is the game of your childhood dreams
snippet.description:
Hypercharge: Unboxed is a classic style FPS game that mixes Tower Defense with Wave-Based Shooting. It has a huge focus on teamwork, exploration and progression. Break free from your packaging (literally) and blast every toy to pieces! Leave a like if you enjoy the video and subscribe for more. Thanks for watching!

Subscribe! https://bit.ly/Subscribe2Tomographic
